'''迈克尔·安德鲁·霍利克'''（{{Lang-en|Michael Andrew Hollick}}，{{Bd|1973年|8月5日}}），美国男演员，知名于为电子游戏《[[侠盗猎车手IV|侠盗猎车手IV]]》的主角[[尼克·本立克|尼克·本立克]]配音。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=A Video Game Star and His Less-Than-Stellar Pay (Published 2008)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/21/arts/television/21gta.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2008-05-21|accessdate=2020-12-31|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Seth|last=Schiesel|archive-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331134847/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/21/arts/television/21gta.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Niko's voice earned about $100,000 from GTA IV|url=https://www.engadget.com/2008-05-21-nikos-voice-got-about-100-000-for-gta-iv-and-not-a-penny-more.html|accessdate=2020-12-31|work=Engadget|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231093915/https://www.engadget.com/2008-05-21-nikos-voice-got-about-100-000-for-gta-iv-and-not-a-penny-more.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 演艺事业 ==
在出演《侠盗猎车手IV》前，霍利克曾于[[百老汇|百老汇]]内[[外百老匯|外]]出演多部话剧，<ref>{{Cite news|title=Don’t Slump: Stand, Gawk, Collaborate (Published 2007)|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/25/theater/reviews/25fuer.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2007-10-25|accessdate=2020-12-31|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Charles|last=Isherwood|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231093914/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/25/theater/reviews/25fuer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Theater Review; Odd Brits A-Leaping With Bodies Or Brains|url=http://theater.nytimes.com/mem/theater/treview.html?html_title=Jumpers%20%28Play%29&tols_title=Jumpers%20%28Play%29&byline=Ben%20Brantley&pdate=20040426&id=1078134675669|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2020-12-31|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|author=|date=|work=|publisher=|format=|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231093914/https://www.nytimes.com/section/theater?html_title=Jumpers+%2528Play%2529&tols_title=Jumpers+%2528Play%2529&byline=Ben+Brantley&pdate=20040426&id=1078134675669|dead-url=no}}</ref>并于《法律与秩序：特殊受害者》《欲望都市》等剧中饰演配角，<ref>{{Cite news|title=Movies|url=https://www.nytimes.com/section/movies|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2020-12-31|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104192611/http://movies.nytimes.com/person/65591/Gregory-Sierra|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Anchors Away|url=https://seplis.net/sex-and-the-city/episode/anchors-away/202925/|accessdate=2020-12-31|author=|date=|format=|work=seplis.net|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231093913/https://seplis.net/sex-and-the-city/episode/anchors-away/202925/|dead-url=no}}</ref>于[[音乐剧|音乐剧]]《{{Le|狮子王 (音乐剧)|The Lion King (musical)|狮子王}}》中为角色[[刀疤|刀疤]]配音。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Life as Uncle Scar in The Lion King — and Scar's new baby|url=http://www.lasvegassun.com/news/2010/aug/05/life-uncle-scar-em-lion-kingem----and-scars-new-ba/|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Las Vegas Sun|language=|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20130127222851/http://www.lasvegassun.com/news/2010/aug/05/life-uncle-scar-em-lion-kingem----and-scars-new-ba/|archivedate=2013-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《侠盗猎车手IV》发售后，霍利克因薪酬问题与制作公司[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]]发生了争议。该游戏的总销售额多达6亿美元，而霍利克只收入了10万美元。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Grand Theft Auto IV Voice: I've Been Robbed! (TTWO)|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/2008/5/the-voice-of-grand-theft-auto-iv-voices-his-displeasure-with-pay-ttwo-|accessdate=2020-12-31|last=Sridharan|first=Vasanth|work=Business Insider|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231093918/https://www.businessinsider.com/2008/5/the-voice-of-grand-theft-auto-iv-voices-his-displeasure-with-pay-ttwo-|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
霍利克的配偶是演员安琪拉·蔡（Angela Tsai），于2007年成婚。两人有一双儿女，分别名为麦克斯韦（Maxwell）和艾娃（Eva）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Unexpected birth of 'Lion King' actor's son is drama to the Max - Las Vegas Sun Newspaper|url=https://lasvegassun.com/blogs/kats-report/2010/jul/22/unexpected-birth-lion-king-actors-son-drama-max/|accessdate=2020-12-31|date=2010-07-22|last=Katsilometes|first=John|work=lasvegassun.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231093946/https://lasvegassun.com/blogs/kats-report/2010/jul/22/unexpected-birth-lion-king-actors-son-drama-max/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

霍利克曾于[[卡耐基梅隆大学|卡耐基梅隆大学]]就读，并在那里获得了{{le|美术学士|Bachelor of Fine Arts}}学位。<ref>{{Cite web|title=About Michael Hollick|url=http://www.michaelhollick.com/bio.html|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218101714/http://michaelhollick.com/bio.html|archivedate=2015-02-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

